title: Be'er Avraham : perush ṿe-hagahot ʻal mekhilta, meha-Tana Rabi Yishmaʻel ... / hishʾir ... Avraham mi-Slonima... devaraṿ sovevim ... ʻal ...divre ha-perush zeh yenaḥamenu / [me-et Mosheh ben Shimʻon Franḳfurṭer] ... ke-fi she-nidpas be-Amsṭerdam ʻa.y. ha-meḥaber.
